Enum LcdDesign

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LcdDesign>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<LcdDesign>

    public enum LcdDesign
extends java.lang.Enum<LcdDesign>
    Color definitions for different LCD designs. Some of the colors are taken from images of real lcd's which really leads to a more realistic look of the lcd display.
